/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拍咗年半次次都單機食飯 覺得冇乜嘢 <br />\n佢有佢玩 我有我玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有時會㗳下嗲 之後2個人又開始玩手機<br />\n起身走先開始多嘢講</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地會有共識出黎見唔用電話<br />\n如果用嘅話都係上連登搵話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時重用唔夠電話？一齊都要咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁不如skype直播大家食飯算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依個咪就係我嬲既原因<br />\n食飯都要各自修行 各自玩手機 有乜謂<br />\n當然我郁啲閪佢面我都有錯<br />\n但係條柒頭一食完唔撚理我 自己走左去返屋企<br />\n我最撚憎就係佢依樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁每對情侶都有各自相處模式嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地覺得一齊最舒服狀態係食嘢時靜靜地玩手機 <br />\n食完就收埋手機 唔再玩有返交流<br />\n其他情侶未必會咁嫁嘛 有啲可能會覺得唔尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好睇你地兩個相處模式同點諗嫁姐 <br />\n真係唔鐘意當然要傾 揾個最好相處方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a207acab782a7b2b59a9d85df3dac51ff5cab171","tid":139362,"uid":13960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都見過一枱，一男一女可以冇交流，到走果陣先講下野拖下手咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉屌喺咪我嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為同男朋友講咩佢都唔會應我"},{"pid":"2698bcf644f3393046383c6fc68475dfad545238","tid":139362,"uid":776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a447ef754b13abb8036521109bd78df2760e6c9","tid":139362,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"我嗰個都係咁"},{"pid":"d9389ddbd79b2dfff7bfe6d943b7d6a6fc578676","tid":139362,"uid":13952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"屌佢老豆 我依家同佢一齊住緊<br />\n依家一鬧交就叫我搬返屋企住<img src