<br />\nx3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同朋友出街都成日遇到呢個問題，對住朋友又唔想黑面，難得約到一齊出黎吹下水，點解仲要掛住玩手機呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25c7e54221e3e4c5acfb44d2e9fda881bd4259a","tid":139362,"uid":33133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:11:39.000Z","msg":"好有共鳴！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一坐低食飯 一係打機 一係上YouTube睇片 一係碌facebook 大佬識唔識尊重？ 話極都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最尷尬係隔離枱有講有笑 我就自己坐係到一路食野一路望住佢打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你要打機要上youtube睇片可唔可以等我唔係到先？點解次次都要我坐係到睇你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有一次食完飯趕時間 佢話鋪機唔停得 要我坐係到等佢 我就坐係到等左佢半個鐘 仲夠膽話我西佢面趕住走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係除左呢樣佢又真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1e141bfdf51f54942205c0e73b86f44f2b4772","tid":139362,"uid":29670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拍咗年半次次都單機食飯 覺得冇乜嘢 <br />\n佢有佢玩 我有我玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有時會㗳下嗲 之後2個人又開始玩手機<br />\n起身走先開始多嘢講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我拍左三年幾都係咁 睇你個人接唔接受囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己個人好無所謂既 唔會因爲咁樣發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab81b48a9908a5ba1f9d335749bb07b84546deb0","tid":139362,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:21:44.000Z","msg":"我女朋友打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一次屌柒佢 問佢同我食飯定打機 <br />\n<br />\n佢即刻喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後又要我氹返佢"},{"pid":"7462f11832420961d329f