assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌，我會同我男朋友一齊打<br />\n隻game仲要我叫佢同我玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩先同佢一路食飯一路打，死左先爬啖飯食下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地好似好唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f25cfca4ead1668a5f97ddd7ad642dd1890198a","tid":139362,"uid":66465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T17:59:37.000Z","msg":"我女朋友又係咁 <br />\n雖然日日見住<br />\n但佢玩手機玩唔停 <br />\n行街玩搭車玩食飯玩<br />\n最過份連訓教都開住部手機黎掛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔明點解玩on9手機game都上左癮咁<br />\nIpad 手機 舊手機玩成幾個唔同ac<br />\n係街唔拖住佢佢會撞柱<br />\n同佢講佢又話我發癲<br />\n話我控制狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}